item.title: Indian Premier League so far.
item.author: senthil.thyagarajan@gmail.com (Senthil Thyagarajan)
item.description: Indian Premier League(IPL) has had 13 different teams over the past ten years. In this project I have tried to visualize how these teams have performed over the years.
